CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 25, 1959, pg. 13 reads: "Juvenile Court - Pronty L. Ford, clerk-bookkeeper on the Prothonotary's staff in Juvenile Court."
TitMainTitle: Clerk Pronty L. Ford wearing eyeglasses, seated at desk examining documents, in Allegheny County Prothonotary office with brick walls and venetian blinds
